<h2>Revenue Comparison: Real Numbers</h2>
<h3>Case Study: 2-Bedroom Condo in Melaka Raya</h3>
<p><strong>Property Details:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Size: 900 sq ft</li>
<li>Location: Near Melaka Sentral</li>
<li>Market Value: RM 350,000</li>
</ul>
